Customize

Put in your own grfx and text in the pirate box web pages
Set up the shared content directories and sym link them
Add a USB drive

I have added these two lines to /etc/vlc/start.sh because reasons, mostly it works this way all of the time without fail. I should really add these to cron maybe? ymmmv
  sudo service hostapd start 
  sudo mount -o uid=pi,gid=pi /dev/sda1 /media/usb
